OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FITV News Reporter Anna Youssef saw
OL,7,Fsome of the places where young people
OL,8,Fhave been sleeping, despite studying,
OL,9,Fworking and earning.
OL,11,FMany young people are being forced to
OL,12,Fstay in 24-hour McDonalds, use night
OL,13,Fbuses, or set up home in A&Es,
OL,14,Fairports and even an abandoned tomb
OL,15,Fjust to stay warm as they struggle to
OL,16,Fmake ends meet, it has been claimed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
