OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FYouth homeless charity Centrepoint say
OL,7,Fit is seeing more and more young
OL,8,Fpeople in Manchester sleeping rough in
OL,9,Fthe unconventional places, despite
OL,10,Fstudying, working and earning.
OL,12,FOne college student - Hakim - became
OL,13,Fhomeless after he got his immigration
OL,14,Fstatus approved.
OL,16,FHe spent a winter sleeping rough in a
OL,17,Ffield while studying at college and
OL,18,Fhaving treatment for TB.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
