FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772129063
OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FHe said: "It was really really so bad
OL,7,Ffor me by then because it was too cold
OL,8,Fby then in the winter. I was frozen.
OL,10,F"I mean I can't even tell because I
OL,11,Fwas in such a bad life. It was so
OL,12,Fdreadful for me by then."
OL,14,FCentrepoint helped Hakin find
OL,15,Faccommodation and he is now training
OL,16,Fto be a plumber while working part
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,FHe said: "I don't know if I would be
OL,20,Fliving anymore. I was depressed. I was
OL,21,Fso anxious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772129063
OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,F"When Centrepoint intervened
OL,7,Feverything changed. They changed my
OL,8,Flife - that's what I can say. They
OL,9,Fsaved my life."
OL,11,FThe charity works with 18-25-year-olds
OL,12,Fto help them off the streets and into
OL,13,Fsafe accommodation.
OL,15,FRough Sleeper Coordinator Taylor
OL,16,FWoodcock said they have found young
OL,17,Fpeople sleeping rough in a range of
OL,18,Fareas, sometimes amongst rats, food
OL,19,Fwaste and rubbish.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
