OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772129063
OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FHe said: "They would come here at
OL,7,Fnight and they would bed down and
OL,8,Frough sleep here because it was the
OL,9,Fonly place they could find that they
OL,10,Ffelt safe in.
OL,12,F"They're the extremes people are
OL,13,Fforced to go to to try and find a
OL,14,Fplace of safety"
OL,16,FTaylor said he had even seen one case
OL,17,Fof a young person sleeping inside an
OL,18,Fold tomb to try and get some shelter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
