FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772129063
OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FHe said: "We've literally seen a young
OL,7,Fperson bedding down under a tree in
OL,8,Fbitterly cold temperatures in the
OL,9,Fwinter.
OL,11,F"Having to get up in the morning and
OL,12,Fgo to college after rough sleeping
OL,13,Fthere - that's the reality of young
OL,14,Fpeople rough sleeping in Manchester."
OL,16,FThe charity says the main reason for
OL,17,Fyouth homelessness is that rent is
OL,18,Funaffordable for young people - who
OL,19,Ftend to be on lower wages and get more
OL,20,Finsecure work or have zero hour
OL,21,Fcontracts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
