OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772129063
OL,3,C'I was frozen': Young people sleeping
OL,4,Crough despite working and earning
OL,6,FTaylor said: "It's a needle in a
OL,7,Fhaystack and then you throw in if you
OL,8,Fare rough sleeping if means you don't
OL,9,Fhave a support network that can help
OL,10,Fyou out during tough time".
OL,12,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
